===message:Keri, Lord Acton, once said that “Power tends to corrupt, and absolute power corrupts absolutely. Great men are almost always bad men.”  This quotation sums up what you were saying about man’s need for power.  I totally agree with you.  You see this corruption between the sexes, races, and religious sects.  When are people going to grow up and stop this selfishness?  Many political leaders do not promote confidence in the people they rule.  Rather they instill a fear or hatred of others.  This justifies many acts of aggression that need not take place.  We all must see beyond our political barriers and recognize that we all depend on one another and we are all interrelated.
